end_step=model.step_count
start_step=token.data['start_step']
time = end_step-start_step


avg_process = model.instance_base.findByName("平均运行时间")
total = avg_process.amount*avg_process.quota_dscp


avg_process.amount = avg_process.amount+1
avg_process.quota_dscp = (total+time)/avg_process.amount


avg_cost=model.instance_base.findByName("平均运行成本")
process_cost= token.data['cost']
total_cost=avg_cost.amount*avg_cost.quota_dscp
avg_cost.amount=avg_cost.amount+1
avg_cost.quota_dscp = (total_cost+process_cost)/avg_cost.amount

avg_CoopTime = model.instance_base.findByName("警务协同时间")
process_CoopTime = token.data['CoopTime']
total_CoopTime = avg_CoopTime.amount*avg_CoopTime.quota_dscp
avg_CoopTime.amount = avg_CoopTime.amount+1
avg_CoopTime.quota_dscp = (total_CoopTime+process_CoopTime)/avg_CoopTime.amount
